episodes.title: Actress Giovannie Espiritu opens up on former life in Philippine cult
episodes.description:
A Filipino actress and filmmaker who, at one point in her life, was ensnared by a cult, speaks about the experience. As Giovannie Espiritu tells Yong Chavez in this report, that chapter eventually became the starting point for her career in the film industry.
